trans-unit.source: The SignerInfoEnumerator class provides enumeration functionality for the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfoCollection"></xref> collection.
trans-unit.target: SignerInfoEnumerator 클래스에 대 한 열거형 기능을 제공 된 <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfoCollection"> </xref> 컬렉션입니다.

trans-unit.source: The Current property retrieves the current <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfo"></xref> object from the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfoCollection"></xref> collection.
trans-unit.target: 현재 속성은 현재 검색 <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfo"> </xref> 에서 개체는 <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfoCollection"> </xref> 컬렉션입니다.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfo"></xref> object that represents the current signer information structure in the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfoCollection"></xref> collection.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfo"> </xref> 에 현재 서명자 정보 구조를 나타내는 개체의 <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfoCollection"> </xref> 컬렉션입니다.

trans-unit.source: The MoveNext method advances the enumeration to the next <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfo"></xref> object in the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfoCollection"></xref> collection.
trans-unit.target: MoveNext 메서드 다음으로 열거형 진행 <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfo"> </xref> 개체는 <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfoCollection"> </xref> 컬렉션입니다.

trans-unit.source: This method returns a bool value that specifies whether the enumeration successfully advanced.
trans-unit.target: 이 메서드는 열거형이 성공적으로 이동 하는지 여부를 지정 하는 부울 값을 반환 합니다.

trans-unit.source: If the enumeration successfully moved to the next <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfo"></xref> object, the method returns <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 열거형에서 다음 단계로 이동 했으면 <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfo"> </xref> 개체, 메서드는 반환 <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: If the enumeration moved past the last item in the enumeration, it returns <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 반환 하는 경우 열거형이 열거형의 마지막 항목을 지 나 이동, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: The Reset method resets the enumeration to the first <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfo"></xref> object in the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfoCollection"></xref> collection.
trans-unit.target: Reset 메서드 열거형 첫 번째를 기본값으로 다시 설정 <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfo"> </xref> 개체는 <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfoCollection"> </xref> 컬렉션입니다.

trans-unit.source: The IEnumerator.Current property retrieves the current <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfo"></xref> object from the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfoCollection"></xref> collection.
trans-unit.target: IEnumerator.Current 속성 검색 현재 <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfo"> </xref> 에서 개체는 <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfoCollection"> </xref> 컬렉션입니다.
